    <div class="toc-ref">
    
        <ol class="toc"><li class="toc-item toc-level-2"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E6%B3%A8%E5%86%8C-OAuth-Application"><span class="toc-text">注册 OAuth Application</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-2"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8-gitment-%E8%AF%84%E8%AE%BA%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F"><span class="toc-text">使用 gitment 评论系统</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-2"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E5%B9%B6%E5%88%9D%E5%A7%8B%E5%8C%96"><span class="toc-text">部署并初始化</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-2"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E6%84%9F%E5%8F%97"><span class="toc-text">感受</span></a></li></ol>
    
